premise_source_doc_sentence: The 79th Academy Awards ceremony , presented by the Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences  (  AMPAS  )  , honored the best films of 2006 and took place February 25 , 2007 , at the Kodak Theatre in Hollywood , Los Angeles beginning at 5:30 p.m. PST / 8:30 p.m. EST. .
